author: leif
msg: Update the Wrapper configuration file to version 2.2.7  Should still work with older
versions of the Wrapper.  They will just ignore the newer properties.

author: leif
msg: Add some additional state tracking so that Phoenix will shutdown cleanly with
Wrapper version 2.2.7.  The Wrapper had some bug fixes with shutdown isses and
it was showing an error because Phoenix was recursively calling its stop method.

author: donaldp
msg: Add a guard so that connection that does not get a chance to
start before dispose() is shutdown rather than causing hang.
